# GitHub Linguist — language statistics tuning
# Goal: reflect the actual project (TypeScript app + Python translation engine).
# Marketing assets, generated files, and tooling scripts shouldn't count as "the project".

# --- Marketing assets (Fanbox/Patreon page designs, automation) ---
marketing/**          linguist-vendored
marketing/**/*.html   linguist-vendored
marketing/**/*.js     linguist-vendored
marketing/**/*.md     linguist-documentation

# --- Documentation ---
docs/**               linguist-documentation
*.md                  linguist-documentation

# --- Build / packaging scripts (not application logic) ---
scripts/**            linguist-vendored
electron/**           linguist-detectable=true

# --- Generated / vendored ---
package-lock.json     linguist-generated
*.lock                linguist-generated
*.min.js              linguist-vendored
*.min.css             linguist-vendored
build/**              linguist-generated
dist/**               linguist-generated
dist-electron/**      linguist-generated
dist-electron2/**     linguist-generated
.next/**              linguist-generated
out/**                linguist-generated

# --- Line endings (Windows-friendly) ---
* text=auto eol=lf
*.bat text eol=crlf
*.ps1 text eol=crlf
